OL,5, Funding promised to develop the social 
OL,6, care workforce in England has been     
OL,7, halved, the government has confirmed.  
OL,9,FIn 2021 the government pledged "at     
OL,10,Fleast" #500 million for reforms, to be 
OL,11,Fspent on training places and technology
OL,12,Fover three years.                      
OL,14,FBut that figure is now #250 million,   
OL,15,Faccording to the Department of Health. 
OL,17,FA coalition of charities said this cut 
OL,18,Fis "just the latest in a long series of
OL,19,Fdisappointments" over social care.     
